caption.text:
If you’re reading this you’re thinking about solar but you’re probably on the fence. Why? Because it’s so expensive. Or is it? 🤔

We’re Sunsave, a solar energy company on a mission to make solar accessible to all UK households so you can enjoy the benefit of clean, green energy all year round☀️

We’re the first UK company to offer a solar subscription which removes the hefty upfront cost of solar (just over £10,000 eek) replacing with a fixed, manageable monthly fee instead. 

With Sunsave Plus, you can get all the solar kit you need, expert installation and a 20-year guarantee giving you everything you need to get started. 

With solar energy you’ll be able to: 

1️⃣ See instant savings on your energy bill
2️⃣ Rely less on the grid 
3️⃣ Increase your EPC rating 
4️⃣ Sell excess energy back to the grid
5️⃣ Do your bit for the planet 

If you’d like to know what solar would cost you, hit the link in our bio and fill out your details. One of our solar experts will be in touch with a free quote ⚡️
